entries.title: The Race to Build a ChatGPT-Powered Search Engine
entries.description: A search bot you converse with could make finding answers easier—if it doesn’t tell fibs. Microsoft, Google, Baidu, and others are working on it.

entries.title: The Taliban Can’t Stop TikTok
entries.description: Despite an economic crisis, political chaos, and the regime’s ban, TikTok influencers are still thriving in Afghanistan.
